command: Find the space 1 tiles in front
Spawn an object on that spot to check terrain there
This will determine what tile the box will land on before it moves
the code continues on this OBJ's event --->
get new box coords, then y - 1
move the terrain checker object there
in the air, so move down 1 and check again
check if landed on a switch
check if jump tile, then execute
check if landing on a switch
